query:
SELECT id, tenantId, providerType, providerName, isActive, 
  LEFT(accessToken, 50) as token_preview,
  tokenExpiresAt, createdAt, updatedAt 
FROM paymentProviders 
WHERE providerType = 'izettle' 
ORDER BY updatedAt DESC 
LIMIT 1;
